 Alan Mak - former Parliamentary Under Secretary of State, jointly in the Department for Business and Trade and the Cabinet Office - advice under the government’s Business Appointment Rules

 Advice provided to Alan Mak MP, former Parliamentary Under Secretary of State jointly in the Department for Business and Trade and the Cabinet Office, on appointments and employment taken up within two years of leaving office

 From:

