 Advice letter: Alan Mak, Author, Icon Books Limited

 HTML

 Details

 Author, Icon Books Limited

 Mr Mak received advice from the Independent Adviser on Ministerial Standards on taking up a paid commission with Icon Books Limited. The advice was provided in June 2026 and the commission was taken up later that month.

 ACOBA published on its website advice provided to Mr Mak before its closure.

