 Attendees 

 BSL Advisory Board

 Dr Joanna Atkinson, Co-chair of BSL Advisory Board

 Alex Gowlland, Deputy Director of Disability Unit (DU), Cabinet Office (CO), Co-chair

 Matthew Adedeji

 Damian Brewer

 Teri Devine

 Catherine Drew

 Marcella Dwek

 Helen Foulkes

